entry.title: Supreme Court Declines to Fast-Track Trump Immunity Case, as Jan. 6 Looms Over 2024 Election
entry.content: The justices denied special counsel Jack Smith’s request that it bypass a lower court to rule on whether the former president’s election-interference trial can proceed.

entry.title: Israel Hunts for Hamas Leaders in Gaza's Khan Younis
entry.content: As military focuses on the southern city, the United Nations passed a resolution supporting more aid to the enclave.
